    <p>
      Contains: ESG analysis script, pytest tests, synthetic ESG data, data dictionary.
    </p>

    <h3>Contents</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><code>esg_analysis.py</code> — ESG score summary analysis script</li>
      <li><code>test_esg_analysis.py</code> — pytest tests</li>
      <li><code>data/raw/endowment_esg.csv</code> — Synthetic ESG data (15 rows)</li>
